+/// Feed output bytes (e.g. an OSC escape) into the terminal as if read from the pty. Used by the
+/// embedded apprt to push theme colors the renderer otherwise won't pick up from config on this build.
+/// processOutput takes the renderer lock itself, so this is safe to call from the app thread.
+pub fn feedOutput(self: *Surface, data: []const u8) void {
+    self.io.processOutput(data);
